description: Beautiful & Overly Sunny, 2Bed +Office w/2 Full Baths, Private Patio, & GARAGE PARKING at highly sought after PORT 45! This corner unit checks all the boxes. There is a large entryway w/large coat closet when you first enter - this area serves as a great mudroom and also allows you to enter without stepping directly into the living space. The open & airy layout is ideal for entertaining and comfortable living. The kitchen flows seamlessly into a large dining area and living room. The kitchen is highlighted by an oversized, 4-seat island. The kitchen is also equipped with a stainless Bosch appliance package, lots of counter space, gas cooking, and tile backsplash. The bedrooms are on opposite corners of the unit, offering maximum privacy.  Both bedrooms offer walk-in closets and en-suite baths. The secondary bath is also accessible off the living space. The unit also offers a large office, central AC, laundry in unit, and a large patio overlooking the well manicured courtyard. Must see!
